  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为猴子建立一个类模型。猴子最核心的一组行为应该包括吃东西、跳跃，还有那种标志性的咀嚼动作，另外它们受到惊吓时会尖叫。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Monkey",
        "eat",
        "jump",
        "munch",
        "scream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以是一个Monkey类，包含四个方法：eat、jump、munch和scream。我想确认一下，munch和eat有什么区别？是重复了吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Monkey",
        "eat",
        "munch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "不重复。eat是通用的进食行为，munch特指那种大声咀嚼、磨碎食物的动作，是猴子很有辨识度的特征。这两个都要保留。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "eat",
        "munch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，区分清楚了。那我现在开始绘制：一个Monkey类，下面列出eat()、jump()、munch()、scream()这四个方法。顺序就按您说的来？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Monkey",
        "eat",
        "jump",
        "munch",
        "scream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "顺序没问题。不过我突然想到，跳跃jump应该放在第二位比较合理，体现猴子好动活泼的特质，然后是吃相关的，最后是情绪表达。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "jump",
        "eat",
        "munch",
        "scream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，调整好了。现在Monkey类的方法是：jump()排在第二位，然后是eat()、munch()，最后是scream()。您看一下这样呈现可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Monkey",
        "jump",
        "eat",
        "munch",
        "scream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说错了。还是保持最初的顺序吧：eat()、jump()、munch()、scream()。按功能分组更清晰——吃相关的前两个，动作一个，情绪一个。跳跃放第二位反而打乱了逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "eat",
        "jump",
        "munch",
        "scream"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "收到，已恢复为原始顺序：eat()、jump()、munch()、scream()。Monkey类的结构现在定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Monkey",
        "eat",
